title: Ep. #59 | Catching Up: James Lee (BONUS)
description:
Singer James Lee joins Eric to discuss the message behind his new Castles EP, his journey from bassist to singer/songwriter/producer, and lessons learned from "the most defining experience of his life."


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
